abstract: New Zealand defeats Namibia, 58-14, in rugby.
lead_paragraph: New Zealand, the world champion, ran in nine tries, including two each for wingers Nehe Milner-Skudder and Julian Savea, as it powered to a 58-14 win over Namibia.

headline.main: Second-String All Blacks Team Drubs Namibia
